description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Geriatric Nurse to join the K&amp;W Healthcare, CPMG (Complex Patients Management Group) team, to support the management of patients with complex needs. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be a highly motivated, innovative, compassionate and enthusiastic registered nurse, who strives to deliver person-centred care, supported by excellent clinical knowledge and skills, is able to work autonomously and is confident in their own decision making. You must have at least 3 years’ experience working within the speciality, managing patients with long term conditions. You will work collaboratively within the Primary Care Network project and with our member practices, based in Brent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The rate on offer spans between &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;£21-£30/hour&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; depending on experience and qualifications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you feel that your previous skills and experience meet the criteria seen above and in the attached job description, then we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
